{"tid":1598470,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"行街發覺狗狗遊樂會有bug","createTime":"2019-09-27T12:58:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T16:34:29.000Z","uid":214735,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"dd1bb219a4eb483ed13ab4dad97e51570b8c732f","tid":1598470,"uid":214735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T12:58:13.000Z","msg":"小弟住太子一帶，成日行經狗狗遊樂會，果度星期六日一車多等位泊，成條西洋菜南街白楊街就塞成，狗會停車場得一個出口仲要響街尾死位，有次只係2-3架車撞左就塞足成個鐘車，你知啦，次次九龍區（e.g.彌敦道，旺角狗局，黃大仙...等等）有活動狗狗會有幾十架EU同狗狗私家車一齊出動，如果果度一塞車成班狗走唔到出嚟就慘慘啦。<br />\n<br />\n揸車差成日撞車既千祈唔好去果度呀！"},{"pid":"d8788ebbe8bd082e3f1bc16cff7fe0522b41d641","tid":1598470,"uid":214735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T12:58:45.000Z","msg":"十連自推開始"},{"pid":"2fd60e41bf7ec5b622d09530a13b45cae2db743f","tid":1598470,"uid":214735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T12:58:57.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"35cd1b516b51d391ff4e1bc28b2e11848321c12d","tid":1598470,"uid":214735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T12:59:10.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"b19225e3f7c8af569f66447de61beacc52d55885","tid":1598470,"uid":214735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T12:59:20.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"8ae7af504b618266ddadbe8ffbad3c910e6de35b","tid":1598470,"uid":214735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T12:59:30.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"7b76e6f60f98e1a94c8e940eb912aa8c4893ab4b","tid":1598470,"uid":214735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T12:59:42.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"294918ea504d440fdb2660c347accb359f52f0c6","tid":1598470,"uid":214735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T12:59:56.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"c9a86804f695ea384838f3de1cb7f6d2da5eb756","tid":1598470,"uid":214735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T13:00:07.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"6625f1ad89851dfeab63cdd2fcd8405bcf4c7709","tid":1598470,"uid":214735